trigger.name: 5F Rack Inlet DELTA-5: {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: Inlet temperature on a computer rack has changed more than 5 F over 5 minutes (Could be going down. Probably going up)

trigger.name: 5F Rack Inlet DELTA-60: {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: Inlet temperature on a computer rack has changed more than 5 F over 1 hour. (Could be going down. Probably going up)

trigger.name: AC Unit In Failture {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: Compressor is off but unit is on. Condensate pan may be full

trigger.name: Rack Inlet over Limit: {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: Inlet temperature on a computer rack is over the limit for all racks

trigger.name: Return Air over Limit: {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: The temperature of the air returning into the AC unit is over the established limit on that unit.

trigger.name: Supply Air over Limit: {HOSTNAME}
trigger.description: The temperature of the air being supplied by the AC unit exceeds the limit set on that unit.
